OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and largely sunny start.
OL,6,FCloud then builds from the west
OL,7,Fthrough the day, with brighter spells
OL,8,Fbecoming more limited through the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Many parts staying dry, but
OL,10,Fa few outbreaks of rain possible,
OL,11,Fmainly in the west. Turning breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy and breezy during the
OL,14,Fevening, with outbreaks of rain or
OL,15,Fdrizzle. Rain perhaps briefly heavier
OL,16,Faround midnight in the northwest.
OL,17,FOtherwise staying dull and damp with
OL,18,Ffurther drizzle.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
