OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy start, with some
OL,6,Fearly drizzle. Some warmer, drier
OL,7,Fintervals developing. The odd heavier
OL,8,Fshower is also possible, before heavy
OL,9,Frain and gusty winds move east through
OL,10,Fthe afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FSunny
OL,13,Fspells and showers Thursday. Cloudier
OL,14,FFriday, but mostly dry, before a
OL,15,Fweakening band of rain spreads east
OL,16,Flater. Sunny spells and showers
OL,17,FSaturday. Warm in any brighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
